Invocation Name: national park alerts
des:
Use this skill to request alerts from many of the beautiful National Parks in the US. This skill gathers all information from the National Park Service and the content is dynamically generated. Currently we support the following National Parks: 
Glacier
Zion
Yosemite
Acadia
Yellowstone
Grand Canyon 
Grand Teton
...with more to come!
